Blackstone May Hire Ex-Bank Proprietary Traders, Les Echos Says

-- B y   T a r a   P a t e l
-- 
2011-03-21T07:08:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/blackstone-may-hire-ex-bank-proprietary-traders-les-echos-says.html
  Blackstone Group LP (BX)  plans to hire
people leaving U.S. banks’ proprietary-trading desks due to new
restrictions on the activity,  Les Echos  reported, citing an
interview with Chairman  Stephen Schwarzman .  Many “talented people” will be leaving the banks,
Schwarzman was quoted as saying, adding that Blackstone plans to
strengthen operations in the are and expects banks to invest
more in its funds.  Schwarzman will be based in Paris for a few months, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tara Patel in Paris at 
 tpatel2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
